        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜香港5月零售額升7.9%  珠寶鐘錶表現最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜香港5月零售額升7.9% 珠寶鐘錶表現最強\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜香港5月零售額升7.9% 珠寶鐘錶表現最強</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府統計處公布，5月<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"零售業\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:零售業;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/零售業\">零售業</a>總銷貨價值臨時估計為338億元，按年上升 7.9%，表現勝預期升6.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當中珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物升幅最勁，按年增加 25.8%，百貨公司貨品銷貨價值升9.2%；電器及其他未分類耐用消費品銷貨價值升13%；超級市場貨品銷貨價值升0.9%；汽車及汽車零件銷貨價值升1.7%；食品、酒類飲品及煙草的銷貨價值則跌0.3%；燃料銷貨價值跌12.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">扣除價格變動後，2026年5月的零售業總銷貨數量的臨時估計較2025年同月上升4.8%。2026年4月的零售業總銷貨數量的修訂估計較2025年同月上升6.5%。與2025年同期比較，2026年首5個月合計的零售業總銷貨數量的臨時估計上升8.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7ab16de6-5223-3854-9373-24556616ac10-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至2026年5月底的3個月，與先前3個月比較，經季節性調整的零售業總銷貨價值的臨時估計上升4.6%，而經季節性調整的零售業總銷貨數量的臨時估計則上升2.2%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府發言人表示，五月零售總銷貨價值按年繼續穩健上升7.9%。大部分零售商主要類別的銷售均有增長。政府預料經濟繼續擴張和本地勞工收入持續增長，加上訪港旅客繼續增加，應有利零售業務。政府將密切監察外圍不確定因素的演變，對本地消費市場潛在的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
