        {
            "title": "歐元區失業率5月持平歷史低位，歐盟統計局數據顯示",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n4V7lK5FGEVaEo9unadsyQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC8B0UB_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐元區\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐元區;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐元區\">歐元區</a>5月份失業率與歷史低位持平，顯示這個擁有21個成員國的貨幣聯盟在伊朗戰爭帶來的不利因素下，就業市場仍具備一定韌性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據歐盟統計局（Eurostat）週四公佈的數據，經季節性調整後，歐元區5月份失業率為6.2%，與4月份持平，略低於經濟學家預測的6.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐元區勞動市場似乎已成功抵禦通脹憂慮帶來的衝擊，而近期通脹壓力趨於緩和的跡象，或將進一步支撐就業市場表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著美國與伊朗於6月簽署臨時和平協議，油價已回落至衝突爆發前的水平。歐洲央行行長克里斯蒂娜·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）本週表示，通脹面臨的上行與下行風險目前「可能比幾週前更趨於平衡」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-060797a0-5e59-3f76-abe0-7b4ab745aa9b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年2月下旬，美以聯軍對伊朗發動攻擊，導致原油價格急劇攀升，一度威脅推高歐元區整體通脹水平，並對區內經濟造成拖累。歐洲央行亦將上述隱憂列為上月決定加息的重要考量因素之一。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%8D%80%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%875%E6%9C%88%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%BD%8E%E4%BD%8D-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E5%B1%80%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA-104738307.html",
